- DAY mode: Camera ON (right column). Main video area shows a placeholder and does NOT show AI clips. You can add/pick words and they will be stored in the left "Words" list.
- NIGHT mode: Camera visually OFF/dim. Main video area shows 3 example AI short clips (click a thumb to "play" placeholder).

Tiny next step for you (STEP 3):
1) Download the ZIP below and replace your current app files with the ones inside, or unzip to a new folder and open index.html.
2) Test Day mode (default) ‚Äî add words and click them; camera should show "Camera On" behavior and the video area should remain a placeholder.
3) Click the üåô/‚òÄÔ∏è toggle to switch to Night mode ‚Äî camera should appear off/dim and the center area should show 3 clip thumbnails. Click a thumbnail to play a sample.
